title: title1
post: We are seeking a Junior Software Developer with a focus on front-end development in Javascript to join the InsuranceMenu team. As a Junior Software Developer you will be working on our agile team to build enhance the web front end, as well as learning server side code in Java/Groovy, SQL. As we are a growing startup you will have the ability to learn a wide range of technologies and work your way towards taking a large responsibility in the software and product development life cycle that will drive InsuranceMenu to continued success
